{"id":650873,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/07/东瓯故人董文正｜鄱阳县抗洪形势严峻，宣传部门/","date":"2020-07-25T16:10:31Z","modified":"2020-07-25T16:10:31Z","title":"东瓯故人董文正｜鄱阳县抗洪形势严峻，宣传部门居然还在唱赞歌？","content":"<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-650874\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650874\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-28-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>鄱阳湖水位突破历史极值，超过1998年那场特大洪水。以鄱阳县为代表的环鄱阳湖地区被洪水围困，许多村庄泡在洪水中。</p>\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\n<p>三联生活周刊报道鄱阳县洪灾的文章《现场∣整个村子都被“秒”了：鄱阳湖抗洪形势有多严峻》可见一斑。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650875\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-3-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-3-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>家住江西省上饶市鄱阳县的桂湖村的黄能先，村子临近鄱阳湖的一条名为昌江的支流。从他家步行不过10分钟，就能到达岸边的圩堤。</p>\n<p>圩堤名叫问桂道，长约10公里。7月以来，昌江水位漫涨，不到7天就就几近与圩堤齐平。黄能先看着不断上涨的水位，隐约有点担心，但又不是很担心——自他记事以来，这个圩堤就从没倒过，哪怕是1998年那场特大洪水。那一年，洪水只是漫过圩堤，桂湖村受损很小，没有被淹。</p>\n<p>7月8日，圩堤垮塌。</p>\n<p>吴明虎做梦都没想到会有这么大洪水。59岁的他说，这个速度远超1998年，江中的水感觉“一下子就过来了，两个晚上就涨满了，（圩堤）3-4天一下子就倒了”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-650876 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-3-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-3-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>作为中国第一大淡水湖，鄱阳湖正面临着一次大考。连绵不绝的雨季之下，鄱阳湖流域水位正在持续上涨。截至7月12日0时，鄱阳湖周边多个水文站超1998年水位，鄱阳湖水位突破有水文纪录以来的历史极值，超过1998年。7月10日，江西启动防汛Ⅰ级应急响应，江西省防汛指挥部预计，鄱阳湖将发生流域性大洪水。</p>\n<p>在鄱阳县，抗洪形势极为严峻。截至7月13日18时，县里有4个水站水位超过警戒线2.4米以上，3站超过1998年的历史最高水位。昌江的古县渡站当日监测，昌江水位达22.38m，超过警戒线2.88m。</p>\n<p>这已是近期连续几日的晴天后出现下降的水位。最高时，昌江水位一度达到23.43米，超过1998年最高位23.18米。问桂道圩、中洲圩先后在7月8日、9日决堤，率先拉响了防汛警报，鄱阳县紧急将防汛应急响应提升至Ⅰ级。</p>\n<p>“整个村子都被‘秒’了。”黄能先说。据统计，仅这次决堤，就导致15000多亩耕地、6个村庄被淹，一共有上万名村民被转移。</p>\n<p>截至7月12日，鄱阳县共有60万人受灾，7万人被紧急转移安置，经济损失超过5.5亿元。</p>\n<p>​昨天，中共鄱阳县委主管的“鄱阳融媒体”在“鄱阳发布”公众号上居然发布了一篇文章，内容令人感到愤怒不已。</p>\n<p>文章题目叫做《抗洪救灾速写∣洪灾也不是一个彻头彻脑的坏东西……》</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650877\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-3-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650878\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/5-4-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650879\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/6-1-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>文章虽然已经被删除了，但是还是有手快的网友全文截图了，甚至在微博上有许多官方新闻媒体也加入鞭笞的行列。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650880\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/7-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"9343\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/7-1-scaled.jpg 137w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/7-1-16x300.jpg 16w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>“洪灾的恶不全是恶，它也催生了善，你能说它是彻头彻脑的坏东西吗？”</p>\n<p>“特大洪灾……给鄱阳人带来了巨大创伤和深重灾难，但也催化出了许许多多的感天动地的湖城故事，在灾难中重生，在磨砺中崛起，可见，洪灾的恶还不至于坏到透顶。”</p>\n<p>怎么说呢？这种唱赞歌不以为耻，丧事喜办是一直以来的传统。</p>\n<p>汶川大地震后山东省作协副主席王兆山的那首诗有一句“纵做鬼，也幸福”，完全不拿国人的生命当回事，只不过是自己笔下的“投名状”。</p>\n<p>云南省彝良县文联主席陈衍强在新冠疫情期间写诗《仰望天空》，把湖北人当作他在云南驻村扶贫守株待兔的“九头鸟”：</p>\n<p>为防止武汉的疫情蔓延/我在云南彝良/不仅以驻村扶贫的理由/阻止了一个地上的湖北佬/来我家过年的想法/还像伊朗担心无人机一样/随时仰望天空/看是否有九头鸟飞过</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650881\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1-192x300.jpg 192w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1-656x1024.jpg 656w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1-768x1199.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/8-1-984x1536.jpg 984w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>还有6月初广西桂林柳州等地被洪水围困，正经的官媒居然还有心情欣赏“夏日田园风光好”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650882\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/9-1-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650883\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/10-1-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650884\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/11-1-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650885\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/1-29-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650886\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/2-4-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650887\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/3-4-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-650888\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/07/4-4-945x2048.jpg 945w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>当抗洪战士还在前线顶着烈日，冒着酷暑日夜奋战抗洪抢险时；当各地的受灾民众还在救灾安置地点为家园被毁悲痛伤心时；当全国各地群众为江西安徽等受灾地区人民祈祷捐款捐物时；当暴雨还在袭来洪水还没有退却时；不知道“鄱阳发布”这时候写一篇赞扬洪水的文章是脑子坏掉了还是心肠烂掉了？</p>\n<p>都说洪水无情人有情，在“鄱阳发布”看来，洪水有时候也是“有情有义”的！</p>\n<p>Modified on 2020-07-22</p>\n</div>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,38912,38985],"tags":[41147,29551,41256,9863]}